e en toute confiance </strong></span></div></div></div></div></blockquote></div><div style="content-visibility:auto;contain-intrinsic-size:0 112px"><div data-key="3f00a08e0c004cf785867ed2443a9d11" class="r-1oszu61 r-1xc7w19 r-1phboty r-1yadl64 r-deolkf r-6koalj r-1mlwlqe r-eqz5dr r-1q142lx r-crgep1 r-ifefl9 r-bcqeeo r-t60dpp r-xd6kpl r-tskmnb r-1yzf0co r-bnwqim r-417010"><div data-block-content="3f00a08e0c004cf785867ed2443a9d11" class="r-1oszu61 r-1xc7w19 r-1phboty r-1yadl64 r-deolkf r-6koalj r-1ro0kt6 r-eqz5dr r-16y2uox r-1wbh5a2 r-crgep1 r-ifefl9 r-bcqeeo r-t60dpp r-bnwqim r-417010"><div dir="auto" class="css-901oao r-1nf4jbm r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-fdjqy7 r-1xnzce8"><span data-key="ea98bc5be03e4e19aea93d4c562c50b6"><span data-offset-key="ea98bc5be03e4e19aea93d4c562c50b6:0">Le Registre de preuve de covoiturage se positionne comme tiers de confiance entre les oprateurs privs de covoiturage et les collectivits. Lobjectif : mettre en place des outils pour vrifier que les trajets ont bien t raliss et rassurer les collectivits qui proposent des incitations financires. </span></span></div></div></div></div><div style="content-visibility:auto;contain-intrinsic-size:0 160px"><div data-key="1116bd95d26e42898e881225f0c29516" class="r-1oszu61 r-1xc7w19 r-1phboty r-1yadl64 r-deolkf r-6koalj r-1mlwlqe r-eqz5dr r-1q142lx r-crgep1 r-ifefl9 r-bcqeeo r-t60dpp r-xd6kpl r-tskmnb r-1yzf0co r-bnwqim r-417010"><div data-block-content="1116bd95d26e42898e881225f0c29516" class="r-1oszu61 r-1xc7w19 r-1phboty r-1yadl64 r-deolkf r-6koalj r-1ro0kt6 r-eqz5dr r-16y2uox r-1wbh5a2 r-crgep1 r-ifefl9 r-bcqeeo r-t60dpp r-bnwqim r-417010"><div dir="auto" class="css-901oao r-1nf4jbm r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-fdjqy7 r-1xnzce8"><span data-key="458b15ce2f4549e1a69fd17815d6b465"><span data-offset-key="458b15ce2f4549e1a69fd17815d6b465:0">Les dcrets de la Loi dorientation des mobilits (LOM) offrent aux autorits organisatrices de la mobilit (AOM) la possibilit de distribuer directement ou indirectement des incitations financires aux covoitureurs pour encourager la pratique du covoiturage au quotidien. Le Registre de preuve de covoiturage a t cr afin de faciliter la distribution de ces incitations, notamment financires,  travers une certification des trajets,  laide de </span></span><a href="/le-registre-de-preuve-de-covoiturage/classes-de-preuve-and-identite/classes-a-b-c" data-rnw-int-class="link____" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr" style="-webkit-transition-duration:0s;transition-duration:0s"><span data-key="8f58236747554abfb516497febcd92e9" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_265-45832_267-45833-243__"><span data-key="1478ea2fc3ea414da1482c749a8e3a55"><span data-offset-key="1478ea2fc3ea414da1482c749a8e3a55:0">classes de preuve de covoiturage</span></span></span></a><span data-key="f5a310b1fac24596a95a4b99435568c9"><span data-offset-key="f5a310b1fac24596a95a4b99435568c9:0">.</span></span></div></div></div></div><div style="content-visibility:auto;contain-intrinsic-size:0 56px"><div data-key="45eea1c76daa4938891aa86853377299" class="r-1oszu61 r-1xc7w19 r-1phboty r-1yadl64 r-deolkf r-6koalj r-1mlwlqe r-eqz5dr r-1q142lx r-crgep1 r-ifefl9 r-bcqeeo r-t60dpp r-xd6kpl r-1ygmrgt r-1yzf0co r-bnwqim r-417010"><div data-block-content="45eea1c76daa4938891aa86853377299" class="r-1oszu61 r-1xc7w19 r-1phboty r-1yadl64 r-deolkf r-6koalj r-1ro0kt6 r-eqz5dr r-16y2uox r-1wbh5a2 r-crgep1 r-ifefl9 r-bcqeeo r-t60dpp r-bnwqim r-417010"><h3 data-rnw-media-class="__" class="r-1oszu61 r-1xc7w19 r-1phboty r-1yadl64 r-deolkf r-6koalj r-1mlwlqe r-eqz5dr r-1q142lx r-crgep1 r-ifefl9 r-bcqeeo r-t60dpp r-bnwqim r-417010" id="statistiques-en-open-data"><div dir="auto" data-rnw-media-class="213__211" class="css-901oao r-1nf4jbm r-1loqt21 r-fdjqy7 r-1xnzce8"><span data-key="08f28167bf4f468e8ea2d44c942ec369"><span data-offset-key="08f28167bf4f468e8ea2d44c942ec369:0">Statistiques en open data</span></span></div></h3></div></div></div><